libctype — attribution and license
==================================

The implementations in this directory (isdigit.c, isalpha.c,
isalnum.c, isupper.c, islower.c, isspace.c, toupper.c, tolower.c,
and the corresponding MIPS assembly in libctype.asm) are adapted
from musl libc's src/ctype/ subtree.

Source       https://musl.libc.org/
Repository   https://git.musl-libc.org/cgit/musl/tree/src/ctype

